mocp

enter (start song)
space or p (pause)
n (next track)
b (previous track)
tab (switch playlist browsing to filesystem browsing)
a (add one track to the playlist)
d (remove track from the playlist)
C (clear playlist)
. (increase volume 5%)
, (decrease volume 5%)
> (increase volume 1%)
< (decrease volume 1%)
q (quit player)
